## The `tm` package
If using the `tm` package to count the number of reviews containing the word "perfect", be aware that DocumentTermMatrix lowercases all words by default. To make it case-sensitive, you can set the tolower option to FALSE:

<pre>
dtm <- DocumentTermMatrix(corpus, list(dictionary = word.list, tolower = FALSE))
</pre>

There is more information in [this thread](https://www.coursera.org/learn/ml-classification/discussions/hTm_je6KEeWkUAr_DMJ5Lw).
